#ROOM
Vnum     25500
Name     &GCamp Narache&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A small, peaceful encampment of hide tents set in a secluded valley
in southern Mulgore. Young Tauren take their first steps here, guided
by the wisdom of the Earthmother. A large tribal fire burns in the center.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25501
Desc      The golden plains stretch out to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25513 1 25500
  Reset E 1 25512 10 17
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25501
Name     &GCamp Narache - Outskirts&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The grass here is tall, golden, and swaying gently in the warm breeze.
Peaceful plainstriders peck at the seeds, completely ignoring the young
hunters practicing their skills nearby.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25500
Desc      Camp Narache.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25503
Desc      The rolling plains.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25502
Desc      A dark, thorny ravine.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25500 3 25501
  Reset G 1 25500 10
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25502
Name     &GThe Brambleblade Ravine&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A narrow, shadowed ravine heavily overgrown with thick, thorny vines.
Scavenging Palemane Gnolls have set up a crude camp here, constantly
harassing the young braves from Camp Narache.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25501
Desc      The outskirts of the camp.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25511 3 25502
  Reset E 1 25509 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25503
Name     &GThe Golden Plains - South&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The true scale of Mulgore reveals itself. Endless miles of golden grass
roll out toward the horizon. The sky is an incredibly clear, brilliant
blue. Swoops circle overhead, hunting for small prey.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25501
Desc      Camp Narache outskirts.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25505
Desc      The gates of Bloodhoof Village.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25504
Desc      The rocky foothills.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25501 2 25503
  Reset G 1 25501 10
Reset O 0 25514 3 25503
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25504
Name     &GThe Red Rocks&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The golden plains give way to sharp, rust-colored rocky outcroppings.
The shadows here hide deadly Mountain Cougars who use the rocks to
ambush passing caravans.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25503
Desc      The southern plains.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25502 2 25504
  Reset G 1 25502 10
#ENDROOM

