Vnum     25505
Name     &GBloodhoof Village - Gates&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     Two massive, beautifully carved wooden totems mark the entrance to
Bloodhoof Village. Massive Tauren Braves stand guard here, ensuring
the safety of the tribe from quillboars and harpies.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
