#ROOM
Vnum     25506
Name     &GBloodhoof Village - Center&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A bustling, permanent settlement built on the shores of a large lake.
Huge hide tents, curing racks, and roaring fires fill the area. Baine
Bloodhoof stands near the central fire, offering wisdom to his people.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25505
Desc      The village gates.
~
#ENDEXIT
