#ROOM
Vnum     25507
Name     &GStonebull Lake&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A pristine, perfectly still lake providing fresh water for the village.
Massive, thick-hided Kodo Beasts drink peacefully from the shoreline,
their heavy footsteps shaking the ground.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25506
Desc      Bloodhoof Village.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25514 2 25507
  Reset E 1 25511 10 14
Reset O 0 25510 2 25507
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25508
Name     &GThe Golden Plains - Center&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The plains north of Bloodhoof are vast and open. Occasionally, young
hunters spot the incredibly rare pink plainstrider, Mazzranache, darting
through the tall grass here.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    25506
Desc      Bloodhoof Village.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    25512
