~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25512 1 25508
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25509
Name     &GThe Ravaged Caravan&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A Tauren supply wagon lies smashed on the dirt path. Goods are scattered
everywhere, and the draft kodos are missing. Thick, wicked thorns sprout
unnaturally from the ground here, a sure sign of quillboar magic.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25508
Desc      The central plains.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25510
Desc      The quillboar brambles.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25510
Name     &GBristleback Brambles - Entrance&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The golden grass is choked out entirely by massive, razor-sharp thorn
vines. This is the territory of the Bristleback Quillboars. Shamans
patrol the perimeter, tossing earth magic at any who approach.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25509
Desc      The ruined caravan.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25511
Desc      The heart of the brambles.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25505 2 25510
  Reset E 1 25505 10 9
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25511
Name     &GBristleback Brambles - Deep Thorns&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The thorns are so thick they block out the sun, creating a dark,
oppressive fortress. Chief Bloodsear, a massive and scarred quillboar,
sits on a crude throne of stolen goods, commanding his raiding parties.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25510
Desc      The entrance to the brambles.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 25506 1 25511
  Reset E 1 25506 10 16
#ENDROOM

