Vnum     25513
Name     &OThe Venture Co. Mine - Approach&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The beautiful plains are violently scarred here. Trees have been clear-cut,
and the earth is torn up by heavy machinery. The goblins of the Venture
Trading Company have claimed this land by force.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25512
Desc      The northern plains.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    25514
