~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     25514
Name     &OThe Venture Co. Mine - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air is thick with dust and the smell of exhaust. Goblin workers
frantically swing pickaxes, trying to extract precious ores from the
sacred earth of Mulgore as quickly as possible.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
