Vnum     25515
Name     &OThe Venture Co. Mine - Depths&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     Deep underground, a ruthless Venture Co. Supervisor cracks a whip,
demanding more production from his exhausted crew. The operation is
highly illegal and a massive insult to the Tauren.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    25514
Desc      The mine entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
