#ROOM
Vnum     25516
Name     &GThunderhorn Water Well&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A deep, stone-lined well providing precious water to travelers on the
plains. It is carefully maintained by the local tribes and offers a
peaceful spot to rest in the shade of a large tree.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    25517
Desc      The rolling hills.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 25510 2 25516
